{"type": "article", "id": 27732, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-03T06:58:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28540, "name": "Stagg Kettle"}, {"id": 28541, "name": "Valentim"}, {"id": 28542, "name": "Vanity"}, {"id": 28543, "name": "Rabbit Box"}, {"id": 28544, "name": "LYFE"}, {"id": 28545, "name": "Naoto Fukasawa"}, {"id": 28546, "name": "Bruno Peral Bey"}, {"id": 17177, "name": "Sanna Lindstrom"}, {"id": 28547, "name": "Matilda Lindblom"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163710VprHCZumFWRMLjA8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Stagg Kettle by Fellow Design</h2>\n<p>水壶里的水刚刚烧开，这个时候倒水总是有点心惊胆战。Fellow Design 推出的这款 Stagg 烧水壶为此特意设计了一个纤细的出水口，同时还在手柄的顶部增加了一个小平面，让你可以更精确地控制倒水的过程。不仅实用，造型也非常优雅。你还可以通过壶盖上的温度计实时掌控温度。这是它的<a href=\"https://fancy.com/things/1160074961885332359/Stagg-Pour-Over-Kettle\">购买链接</a>，售价为 69 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115457aT6Wkcp18oAXVOsf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115458arC40oIcjlPBf2Xi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021154580JTADUhqXv7izcl3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115458cp1lOTPidukMhRNF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115459ubvK3MqNtkBsO9p6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Valentim by DAM</h2>\n<p>薄荷绿的坐垫搭配木质的沙发架，<a href=\"http://www.dam.pt\">DAM</a> 设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.dam.pt/products/?id=39\">Valentim</a> 的沙发带给人一种清爽的美感，是一个很适合夏天的设计。它的造型灵感来源于阳台的围栏，扶手的靠垫弧度与圆柱形状的胡桃木非常贴合，看起来就像是慵懒地搭在上面一样。这款产品目前还未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115459wDPBxjvmJVUTNYHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115500IGLnAYz8rpC6Uegt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115500n8odWZTGqXhefFbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211550195cjZnDHYwtNz8kV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021155019OeL8R3IUBjFWKf2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ten and ci by Naoto Fukasawa</h2>\n<p>蓝色的天空（ten）与白色的大地（ci），这个扶手椅和茶几的组合由日本设计师 <a href=\"http://www.naotofukasawa.com/\">Naoto Fukasawa</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.driade.com/en/\">Draide</a> 所设计。扶手椅 ten 的靠背微微倾斜，表面的材质还有织布和皮革两种可选。与此呼应的茶几 ci 的桌面由白色大理石制成，纹理使人联想到大地的表面。虽然都是冷色调，但它们的底部都依靠深色的木腿支撑，增添了几分暖色。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115502Ts1m87uMhaBiILel.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47066015\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115502mvnX9fsD0xBNJVgu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115503oJEOSK1nik7dy296.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115503dBLH5n02sxM3ZPoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115504ixNPYBw8gzuT3s47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99022005\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Vanity by Bruno Peral Bey</h2>\n<p>这款很像是一把纸扇的吊灯 <a href=\"http://www.art-tic.com/vanity.html\">Vanity</a> 是西班牙设计师 Bruno Peral Bey 以 50 年代流行的褶皱裙为灵感设计的作品。坚硬光滑的铁质灯架和柔软粗糙的纸质灯罩经过组合，带给人一种简约大气的感觉。在亮灯之后，光线还会因为褶皱产生奇特的光影变化，很适合用作装饰灯。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115504eaM2c6xCNVtqk7Em.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14102564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021155053BUDhzSiPFA09WJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14102564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115505BvTVckwtM3NbyIlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14066496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115506c2zitYqxdObKGQpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13956466\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115506t2MrU6zlmdBx5sHu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1366539\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Rabbit Box by Sanna Lindström</h2>\n<p>Sanna Lindström 和 Matilda Lindblom 是两位充满想象力的设计师，他们联手为孩子设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.sannalindstrom.se/rabbitbox.html\">Rabbit Box</a> 的储物盒或许会让喜欢小动物的成年人都感叹自己被种草。由皮革制成的粉红色“兔耳”实际上是盖子的把手，看上去就好像魔术师从帽子中拉出长长的兔子耳朵一样，非常可爱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115507yQgOpbBve56H3GKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115507Xdpn5arPC4mEyDkc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.6498994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115508Z2nHuX3lFwU7QACS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32686084\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115508ib2MXNly5eR3nmot.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>LYFE by LYFE team</h2>\n<p>我们曾经专门介绍过为空气凤梨（Air Plants）设计的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/18684.html\">一些容器</a>，这种不需要土壤就能生长的植物由瑞典植物学家卡尔·林奈（Carl Linnaeus）在 18 世纪发现，而现在一个来自瑞典的设计团队借鉴了这个概念，推出了一款名为 LYFE 的悬浮花盆，希望重新定义我们的种植方式。LYFE 由一个 12 面体的硅制花盆和橡木底座构成，透露着浓烈的未来科技感。利用内置的磁石，磁悬浮平衡技术可以让花盆悬浮在半空中并且进行 360 旋转，更好地吸收阳光——特别适合空气凤梨。当然，你也可以用 LFYE 进行土壤种植，花盆还暗藏了一个蓄水池防止浇水过量。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flyte/lyfe-set-your-plants-free\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 189 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115508wKHCANTIopG7vljZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021155095M4YL6sSqanJ2mW3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115509wAcnt0Ub4vmyfP9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115510C3atZsEUJ6n8SKLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115510jlMVB39qhx2TAFWu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}